[
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"psasuper\">By <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02734\" class=\"\">fret</st><n id=\"1\" /> when <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">wicked men</st> seem to succeed.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07065\" class=\"\">envy</st> <st data-num=\"06213 05766\">evildoers</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> they will <st data-num=\"04120\" class=\"\">quickly</st> <st data-num=\"05243\" class=\"\">dry up</st> like <st data-num=\"02682\" class=\"\">grass</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"05034\" class=\"\">wither away</st> like <st data-num=\"03418 01877\">plants</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">Trust</st> in the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> and <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st> <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">what is right</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07931\" class=\"\">Settle</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> and <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">maintain</st> your <st data-num=\"0530\" class=\"\">integrity</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Then you will <st data-num=\"06026\" class=\"\">take delight</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and he will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">answer</st> your <st data-num=\"04862 03820\">prayers</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01556\" class=\"\">Commit</st> your <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">future</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">Trust</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in</st> him, and <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">act</st> on your behalf.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He will <st data-num=\"03318 06664\">vindicate</st> you in <st data-num=\"0216\" class=\"\">broad daylight</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06672\" class=\"\">publicly defend</st> your <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">just cause</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01826\" class=\"\">Wait patiently</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03176\">Wait confidently</st><n id=\"2\" /> for him!<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02734\" class=\"\">fret</st> over the apparent <st data-num=\"06743 01870\">success</st> of a sinner,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> who <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">carries out</st> <st data-num=\"04209\" class=\"\">wicked schemes</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07503\" class=\"\">Do not be</st> <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">angry</st> and <st data-num=\"05800 02534\">frustrated</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02734\" class=\"\">fret</st>. That <st data-num=\"0389\" class=\"\">only</st> leads to <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">trouble</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588 07489\">Wicked men</st><n id=\"1\" /> will be <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">wiped out</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but those who <st data-num=\"06960\" class=\"\">rely on</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> are <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">the ones</st> who will <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">possess</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">Evil men</st> will <st data-num=\"05750 04592\">soon</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">disappear</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you will <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">stare</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">at</st> the <st data-num=\"04725\" class=\"\">spot where</st> they <st data-num=\"04725\" class=\"\">once were</st>, but they will <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">be gone</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But the <st data-num=\"06035\" class=\"\">oppressed</st> will <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">possess</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06026 05921\">enjoy</st> <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">prosperity</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">Evil men</st> <st data-num=\"02161\" class=\"\">plot</st> against the <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">godly</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"02786 05921 08127\">viciously attack</st> them.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st> <st data-num=\"07832\" class=\"\">laughs in disgust</st><n id=\"1\" /> at them,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> he <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">knows</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> their <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> is <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">Evil men</st> <st data-num=\"06605\" class=\"\">draw</st> their <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">swords</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"01869\" class=\"\">prepare</st> their <st data-num=\"07198\" class=\"\">bows</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">to <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">bring down</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"06041\" class=\"\">oppressed</st> and <st data-num=\"034\" class=\"\">needy</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and to <st data-num=\"02873\" class=\"\">slaughter</st> those who are <st data-num=\"03477 01870\">godly</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">swords</st> will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">pierce</st><n id=\"1\" /> their own <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">hearts</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and their <st data-num=\"07198\" class=\"\">bows</st> will be <st data-num=\"07665\" class=\"\">broken</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"04592\" class=\"\">little bit</st> that a <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">godly man</st> owns is <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">better</st> than<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"01995\" class=\"\">wealth</st> of <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">many</st> <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">evil men</st>,<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">evil men</st> will <st data-num=\"07665\" class=\"\">lose</st> their <st data-num=\"02220\" class=\"\">power</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05564\" class=\"\">sustains</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">godly</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03045\">watches over</st> the <st data-num=\"08549\" class=\"\">innocent</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day by day</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and they <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">possess</st> a <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">permanent</st> <st data-num=\"05159\" class=\"\">inheritance</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0954\">be ashamed</st> when <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">hard</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">times</st> come;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">when <st data-num=\"07459\" class=\"\">famine</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">comes</st> they will <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">have enough to eat</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">But</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">evil men</st> will <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">die</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st> will be <st data-num=\"03350 03564 03615\">incinerated</st><n id=\"2\" />\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">they will <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">go up</st> in <st data-num=\"06227\" class=\"\">smoke</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">Evil men</st> <st data-num=\"03867\" class=\"\">borrow</st>, but do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07999\" class=\"\">repay</st> their <st data-num=\"07999\" class=\"\">debt</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but the <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">godly</st> <st data-num=\"02603\" class=\"\">show compassion</st> and <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">are generous</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Surely</st><n id=\"1\" /> those <st data-num=\"01288\" class=\"\">favored</st> by the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">possess</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but those <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">rejected</st><n id=\"3\" /> by him will be <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">wiped out</st>.<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">grants</st> <st data-num=\"04703\" class=\"\">success</st> to the <st data-num=\"01397\" class=\"\">one</st><p class=\"poetry\">whose <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">behavior</st> he <st data-num=\"02654\" class=\"\">finds commendable</st>.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Even if</st><n id=\"1\" /> he <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">trips</st>, he will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02904\" class=\"\">fall headlong</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05564\" class=\"\">holds</st><n id=\"3\" /> his <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> once <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young</st>, <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">now</st> I <st data-num=\"02204\" class=\"\">am old</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">never</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">seen</st> the <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">godly</st> <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">abandoned</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">or their <st data-num=\"02233\" class=\"\">children</st><n id=\"1\" /> forced to <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">search for</st> <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> long they <st data-num=\"02603\" class=\"\">show compassion</st> and <st data-num=\"03867\" class=\"\">lend</st> to others,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and their <st data-num=\"02233\" class=\"\">children</st><n id=\"2\" /> are <st data-num=\"01293\" class=\"\">blessed</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">Turn away</st> from <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st>. <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">Do</st> <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">what is right</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Then you will <st data-num=\"07931\" class=\"\">enjoy</st> <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">lasting</st> <st data-num=\"07931\" class=\"\">security</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">promotes</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">justice</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">never</st> <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">abandons</st><n id=\"2\" /> his <st data-num=\"02623\" class=\"\">faithful followers</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They are <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">permanently</st> <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">secure</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but the <st data-num=\"02233\" class=\"\">children</st><n id=\"4\" /> of <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">the wicked</st> are <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">wiped out</st>.<n id=\"5\" /></p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">godly</st> will <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">possess</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st><p class=\"poetry\">and will <st data-num=\"07931\" class=\"\">dwell</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in</st> it <st data-num=\"05703\" class=\"\">permanently</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"06310 06662\">godly</st> <st data-num=\"01897\" class=\"\">speak</st> <st data-num=\"02451\" class=\"\">wise words</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03956 01696\">promote</st> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">justice</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st> of their <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> controls their <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">thinking</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">their<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0838\" class=\"\">feet</st> do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"04571\" class=\"\">slip</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "31"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">The wicked</st> <st data-num=\"06822\" class=\"\">set an ambush</st> for the <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">godly</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">try</st> to <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">kill</st> them.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "32"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05800 03027\">surrender</st> the godly,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> allow them to be <st data-num=\"07561\" class=\"\">condemned</st> in a <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">court of law</st>.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "33"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06960\" class=\"\">Rely</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">on</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">Obey</st> his <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">commands</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Then he will <st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">permit</st> you<n id=\"3\" /> to <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">possess</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">you will <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> the <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">demise</st> of <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">the wicked</st>.<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "34"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I have <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">seen</st> <st data-num=\"06184\" class=\"\">ruthless</st>, <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">wicked people</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05927\">growing in influence</st>, like a <st data-num=\"07488\" class=\"\">green</st> <st data-num=\"0249\" class=\"\">tree</st> <st data-num=\"07488\" class=\"\">grows</st> <st data-num=\"0249\" class=\"\">in its native soil</st>.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "35"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But then one <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">passes by</st>, and <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">suddenly</st> they have <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">disappeared</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">looked for</st> them, but they could <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> be <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">found</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "36"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08104\">Take note of</st> the <st data-num=\"08535\" class=\"\">one who has integrity</st>. <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">Observe</st> the <st data-num=\"03477\">upright</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> who promotes <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">peace</st> has a <st data-num=\"0319\" class=\"\">future</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "37"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06586\" class=\"\">Sinful rebels</st> are <st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">totally</st> <st data-num=\"08045\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">the wicked</st> <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">have no</st> <st data-num=\"0319\" class=\"\">future</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "38"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "37",
